snippet.title: JustAxe — Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Pioneers against aliens!

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2455430/JustAxe/

🪓 JustAxe is an exciting 2D platformer with puzzles, interactive environments and unusual setting! Solve riddles, combine your moves, and set out to save your hometown and possibly all of humanity...And don’t forget to take your axe with you!

🔗 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/justaxegame/ 
🔗 Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/justaxegame/
🔗 Twitter: https://twitter.com/justaxegame/

#justaxe #targemgames
